Share with @andotherstories.

node.text:
It's World Mental Health Day and we are so proud to have teamed up with women's health expert and @loomhq CEO @ericachidi to support our community.

We asked you to share with us how you are feeling about your mental health, your body, struggles and hopefulness. @ericachidi has gone through all of your questions and shared her tools for well being and self care.

Our constant beauty crush @sabletoothtigre takes us on an alluring eye look journey from sand dunes to pink skies in a heartbeat, with our beautifully customised Calypso Nine Eye Shadow Palette featuring four matt colours, two shimmering and three glitter-infused.

Check out our IGTV to get the full look with @sabletoothtigre.
